{
  "stem": "8352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And if somebody will try to run away, will be shot-- punished for that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nobody is supposed to run nowhere, just follow the orders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all start packin' and taking each-- old and young-- the old  people, the young children, all the families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We went to the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when  they cleared up all the homes, they searched all the homes to see if everybody is out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans came in there in 194.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us we shouldn't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would just take us to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we will be well taken care of and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They came in-- when we were all at a school yard, they came in with big trucks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they loaded us up on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to go in those trucks as many as they could push in one of those trucks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us to the nearest railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] From the-- from-- from that-- with those trucks, they took-- they took us to-- they pushed us in in those-- in those freight-- freight trains, like cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took us to Mateszalka, to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were going from all those villages collecting all the Jews putting them on those trains, and those trucks, and then to the train and taking us to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know nowhere where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just throw us in the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were screaming at us, and-- and start to beat us, and pushing us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had to do it fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
